{"tid":799713,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好撚掛住MSN年代","createTime":"2018-08-30T09:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T14:10:57.000Z","uid":36097,"like":206,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"0dad570e6f9bee68f6e2a227a59479681ddd508f","tid":799713,"uid":36097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:49:32.000Z","msg":"玩住勁舞等班fd逐個逐個online 應該係最深刻既事 個陣online game盛行 個個放學衝番屋企打機 MSN不可或缺 所以d group熱鬧到不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 約人出街又一定用MSN 咁岩學生時期節日時候班group或者fd group一定有起碼8至10條友約出街 仲要有囡囡 唔會有毒撚出現 唔似家陣whatsapp又怕人唔覆怕人忙 因為見到你MSN online已經代表可以搵你鳩up 踩地雷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見你耐冇online又會自然打電話搵你 又咁岩smart phone又未盛行 令到你一係坐係屋企就一定用MSN 就算見唔到面都有交流 一係想見面就約出黎又唔會on99咁禁手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個時既友誼先係最真誠 科技同人既交流達到最佳既相輔相乘作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n90後既青春真係前無古人後無來者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到家陣只可以惋惜除左我地呢一代唔會再有人明有MSN既青春係幾咁正 亦冇可能番到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前人唔明科技 後人依賴科技 MSN既功能同出現時期可以話係神一般既結合 百利而無一害 確實促進左人與人交流 又同時冇令交流遜色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同時MSN收皮個一日我都好深刻 印證左90後既青春既沒落..."},{"pid":"0287994043902ff0d43367dfe4cd0f445ef409b2","tid":799713,"uid":198583,"like":13,"dislike":34,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:50:42.000Z","msg":"細個挽msn震9人好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2deb8bc3f00bdabba234278440d8fb6d108027a9","tid":799713,"uid":8175,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"Icq"},{"pid":"707bd1e478729c7e9fb5cc50688dbd92a3bd4483","tid":799713,"uid":16123,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"0287994043902ff0d43367dfe4cd0f44